[img]http://img509.imageshack.us/img509/4189/mybannerglitter5c10e64fde0.gif[/img]
Ok most ppl know that i was the coder and owner of coowhipscape... well since i retired over 3 months ago from coding i was getting bored during the summer with no school... but since i go to work at 6am to 3pm i usually had to much time so me and my hoster thought about making a new server.. this one is a dodian pk server with the most ultimate places... i am willing to give everyone here a sneak peak... but please do not flam or spam this topic over stupid stuff... now here are the pics..
[b][u]Pk Shop-[/u][/b] [img]http://i33.tinypic.com/dfudk6.jpg[/img]
[b][size=10pt]Staff Shop![/size][/b] [img]http://i35.tinypic.com/1t7rc8.jpg[/img]
and for the final picture!!!! [b][u][size=12pt]PK ZONE![/size][/u][/b] [img]http://i37.tinypic.com/66iwp0.jpg[/img] before the fire line.. its 1 on 1 and after the line it is all on all.
----------------------- Ok well since i have not finished it yet and it is mainly a pk server... most of the pics are gonna be of the pk stuff... and the server grand opening 24/7 hosting will be between sunday-next sunday we havnt scheduled the date but when i get the date picked out i will have it up on here... we are hoping to have it with as many players as we use to... which is around 15-40 i has it set so it can hold a maximum of 250 players before lag and crashing starts. If you would like to get a custom saved char file started just pm or send me the char file u would like to have on it. i am creating a custom client after the server... it will not be silabs.. since silabs is gay and is no point in it besides to let every1 have the items.. so if i add items it will be just weapons and capes nothin else... Plz post good replys no spam or flaming plz.
